%% Revised Sequence: Branch Lookup (non-sensitive) with EIDP for Glue fallback
%% Created by GitHub Copilot on 2026-03-01 for ADR-0104 Round 2 Review
%% Shows EIDP token acquisition for Glue-bound calls

sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CES as CX Agent Studio
  participant BFA as BFA Gateway (Cloud Run)
  participant LOC as Location Adapter (internal)
  participant LOCRM as Location Read Model<br/>(curated branches.json)
  participant EIDP as EIDP (Enterprise Identity Provider)
  participant Glue as Glue (WSO2) / Location API

  User->>CES: "Find the closest branch"

  CES->>BFA: Tool call (Service Directory PNA)<br/>IAM ID token (service identity)<br/>headers: request_id, session_id, agent_id,<br/>tool_id, customer_id_hash, auth_level

  Note over BFA: Validate CES identity<br/>Validate mandatory headers<br/>Classify as NON-SENSITIVE (location = public data)

  BFA->>LOC: Internal route to location domain<br/>propagate: all correlation headers

  alt BFA read model has data (Phase 1 primary path)
    LOC->>LOCRM: Deterministic lookup by city/postal code
    LOCRM-->>LOC: Branch list + source version + last_refreshed timestamp
    Note over LOC: No upstream call needed<br/>No EIDP token needed<br/>Fastest path
  else Live location call required (Glue fallback)
    Note over LOC: Glue fallback requires EIDP service token<br/>and verified Interconnect path
    LOC->>BFA: Request EIDP service token<br/>audience: glue-location-api
    BFA->>EIDP: Service token request<br/>(OAuth2 client_credentials over mTLS)<br/>audience: glue-location-api<br/>scope: location.branches.read<br/>(via Cloud Interconnect)
    EIDP-->>BFA: EIDP service token<br/>(short-lived, audience: glue-location-api)
    BFA-->>LOC: EIDP service token
    LOC->>Glue: Query branches/ATMs<br/>Authorization: Bearer {eidp_service_token}<br/>(mTLS via Interconnect)<br/>propagate: correlation headers
    Glue-->>LOC: Branch list
  end

  LOC-->>BFA: Normalized result set (no PII)
  BFA-->>CES: Response + correlation IDs
  CES-->>User: Voice response:<br/>"The nearest branch is at Hauptstraße 12,<br/>open until 6 PM today"
